text: Thomas Woddow (born 3 June 1969) is a German rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Schwedt
